.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3533500/extras/sword.png?t=1739976372\" />\u00a0<strong>Dynamic Combat System</strong> \u2013 Engage in real-time battles with dodges, parries, staggers, and powerful skills like the whirlwind sword attack or wielding primitive black powder firearms!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3533500/extras/Untitled-steam-618-152-971-585-crop-left-971-right-971-top-585-bottom-703-trim-end-7-983333-fps-25-c.gif?t=1739976372\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3533500/extras/relations.png?t=1739976372\" />\u00a0<strong>Meaningful Relationships</strong> \u2013 Forge friendships with the townsfolk, gain unique benefits, and even find romance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3533500/extras/gif4-steam-628-154-966-593-crop-left-966-right-966-top-593-bottom-693-trim-end-7-9-fps-25-colors-90.gif?t=1739976372\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3533500/extras/firends.png?t=1739976372\" />\u00a0<strong>4-Player Co-op Mode</strong> \u2013 Team up with friends to farm, explore, and battle together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3533500/extras/gif5-steam-628-154-966-593-crop-left-966-right-966-top-593-bottom-693-trim-end-7-933333-fps-25-color.gif?t=1739976372\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3533500/extras/tree.png?t=1739976372\" /