 concoctions with unique effects\u2014some requiring ancient rituals to perfect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3533500/extras/gif8-steam-628-154-966-593-crop-left-966-right-966-top-593-bottom-693-trim-end-10-083333-fps-25-colo.gif?t=1739976372\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3533500/extras/wishlist.png?t=1739976372\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Leaforia</strong>, a mysterious town where fate has taken an unexpected turn for you. Caught red-handed for illegally copying and selling books, you now find yourself <strong>paying off a hefty fine</strong> by managing the rundown <strong>farm of old Walter</strong>. As you till the soil and tend to your crops, you uncover a deeper conflict\u2014the townsfolk, devoted protectors of nature, are in a desperate struggle against a band of cursed lumberjacks determined to fell the legendary <strong>Tree of Life</strong>.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3533500?t=1739976372","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3533500?t=1739976372","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3533500/113a4e065cd83543a0a10c2fdfce65914543fc0f/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739976372","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3533500/113a4e065cd83543a0a10c2fdfce65914543fc0f/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739976372","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"LAN Co-op","id":48},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id